      "content": "sometimes i just sit here in this apartment and realize that if i just... stopped existing tomorrow, nothing would actually change. like, i'm just a ghost moving through a city where nobody knows my name and nobody would even blink if i wasn't here. it's like i'm already gone, just going through the motions.",
